body:
Well, I see how everyone complains about the server skin, not full 100% representing our region. 
Why don&#039;t we share some ideas on how the skin could possibly have turned out?

For me, I do like the blue, but I feel as if instead of the skin representing the Southern Cross, it should represent the ocean more.
Because, Oceanic relates closely to the ocean.  I have a few idea&#039;s that could be taken on board, for different champions, that can still represent our region specifically. 

- Octopus Vel&#039;Koz {an obvious one}
- Coral Thief Zyra {instead of thorns, using coral and seaweed}
- Manatee Bard? {clearly this is a stupid thought, but who knows}
- Fisherman Wukong or Yorick{fishing rod as his stick?}
- Polar Bear Volibear {probably not a great one}

Only ideas but I feel as if the oceanic region can be brought out more, if the skin was connected more to its marine life. And even if you want it to still be for charity, it can go towards charities who try to preserve places like the Great Barrier Reef.

What do you guys think? If it ever were to change should it be more Oceanic? I don&#039;t know much I&#039;m just a simple man.
